				<td colspan="2"><span>Greeting Fellow Bards,
<br />

<br />
I have read alot about PvP and it seem that only suggestions about PvPing are for 50+ bards.  I have heard that bards sux at PvP until high 50s to 60s.
<br />

<br />
I would love to get some suggestions about PvP for lower level bards.  I play on the PvP diety server and cant seem to stand toe to toe with an even con.  I am currrently lvl 34.
<br />

<br />
Thanks for any help you can provide.
<br />

<br />
Mystrocat
<br />
Bard of 34 Seasons
<br />
Sullon Zek</span></td>
